*** Goal ***
The exercise is to write a command line driven text search engine. For detailed description see pdf file.


*** Build ***
The project contains Maven config for testing and packaging the application.
Otherwise no 3rd party libraries are required to run the application.


*** How to use ***
java -jar SchibstedSearch.jar /path/to/directory/containing/text/files
Type search phrases in interactive prompt or :quit to stop.


